["Refresh their rotation with these children's Tensaur Sport trainers from adidas. Comin' in a Core Black colourway, these sneaks are made with smooth synthetic leather in the upper for durable wear. ["Get a sleek look that's drippin' with retro style in these juniors' Ozweego sneakers from adidas Originals. In a black colourway, these creps take inspo from the OG '98 Ozweego sneakers. Made with a mesh upper to keep your feet cool, they come with suede overlays for essential support and style.  With tonal lacing for a locked-in fit, these sneakers are sat on an EVA midsole that has Adiprene cushioning to the forefoot and heel for a responsive ride. With a grippy rubber outsole to keep you steppin', these trainers are finished with 3-Stripes to the sidewalls, along with the iconic Trefoil to the tongue. Please Note: Ozweego fit small, we recommend sizing half a size up from your regular size.|EE7775", 'Care & Material', 'Leather & Textile Upper/Synthetic Sole', 'Colour:', 'Black', 'Product Code: 149376/149376', ' ']
